---
title: Herby Crumbed Chicken & Potato Fries with Apple Salad & Mayonnaise
description: Boost the flavour of a classic chicken schnitzel by adding parsley to the golden crumb coating. Served with garlic
aioli, potato fries and a crisp salad for a meal nobody can refuse!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/652f254e19da7d8129dcef6c-677ee97c.jpeg
